628
00:59:51,671 --> 00:59:54,382
- Pengotor!
- Langau!

629
00:59:54,465 --> 00:59:57,176
Penyakit anjing gila
tak boleh disebarkan manusia.

630
00:59:59,304 --> 01:00:02,181
Buku <i>Bangsawan Lalat</i>
bukan menceritakan serangga.

631
01:00:02,849 --> 01:00:05,435
